Code Examples from the course

    Try to avoid nested functions
    function sumOfSquares(x, y) {
      // This will repeatedly be parsed.
      function square(n) {
        return n * n;
      }
    }

    return square(x) + square(y);

A better representation of the above would be
    function square(n) {
      return n * n;
    }
    function sumOfSquares(x, y) {
      return square(x) + square(y);
    }
    
    

